"{\"uid\": \"gothamist.com-news-how-the-viral-olympic-village-muffins-ended-up-at-an-east-village-caf%C3%A9\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published Aug 23, 2024 Modified Aug 24, 2024 Share Published Aug 23, 2024 Modified Aug 24, 2024 Share Make your contribution now and help Gothamist thrive in 2025.Donate today Gothamist is funded by sponsors and member donations At a glance, it might just look like a double chocolate chip muffin - albeit a really good-looking one.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 340, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aug\", \"from\": 10, \"to\": 13}, {\"ngram\": \"2024 Share\", \"from\": 40, \"to\": 50}, {\"ngram\": \"your contribution\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 124}, {\"ngram\": \"2025.Donate today\", \"from\": 158, \"to\": 175}, {\"ngram\": \"Gothamist\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 185}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsors\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 207}, {\"ngram\": \"member donations\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 228}, {\"ngram\": \"a glance\", \"from\": 232, \"to\": 240}, {\"ngram\": \"a double chocolate chip muffin\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But to the chronically online, it's the pastry that took TikTok by storm when Norwegian swimmer Henrik Christiansen posted videos raving about the delicious treats.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.175593249773193e-38, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}, {\"begin\": 420, \"end\": 429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.8730900556153663, \"rank\": 0.14257998611722536, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.6621615443867334, \"rank\": 0.5102040816327192, \"text\": \"Henrik Christiansen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pastry\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"storm\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"videos\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 471}, {\"ngram\": \"the delicious treats\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Internet users became obsessed with trying them.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Internet users\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So when East Village caf\\u00e9Isshiki Matchaannouncedit had gotten its hands on the muffins and would host a one-day pop-up sale on Saturday, Aug. 17, people began lining up at 6 a.m. - four hours before the sale began.\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 565, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Village,_Manhattan\", \"score\": 0.9968205661580373, \"rank\": 0.0010645904504647525, \"text\": \"East Village\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Village,_Manhattan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Village,_Manhattan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its hands\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"the muffins\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 643}, {\"ngram\": \"a one-day pop-up sale\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"the sale\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Isshiki sold out of the muffins, valued at $10 a pop, in just an hour-and-a-half.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 772, \"end\": 779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"score\": 0.9999999568408393, \"rank\": 3.9629404640167504e-08, \"text\": \"Isshiki\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the muffins\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 803}, {\"ngram\": \"just an hour-and-a-half\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But getting the muffins to Isshiki wasn't so simple.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 882, \"end\": 889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"score\": 0.9999999568408393, \"rank\": 3.9629404640167504e-08, \"text\": \"Isshiki\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the muffins\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It started when Kelin Carolyn Zhang, a Brooklyn-based designer who was previously unaffiliated with Isshiki, saw videos of the muffins and decided she needed to try them.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/We_Stitch_These_Wounds\", \"score\": 0.9923596880625373, \"rank\": 0.003832504159597565, \"text\": \"Carolyn\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/We_Stitch_These_Wounds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/We_Stitch_These_Wounds\"}, {\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"score\": 0.9999999568408393, \"rank\": 3.9629404640167504e-08, \"text\": \"Isshiki\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Brooklyn-based designer\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"videos\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"the muffins\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So she got to work on figuring out which company supplied them, and brainstormed with other TikTok users.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1172, \"end\": 1178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.175593249773193e-38, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"which company\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was like, OK, this seems still so much more attainable than me going to the Olympics and eating a muffin as an Olympic athlete,\\\" she told Gothamist.\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1274}, {\"ngram\": \"a muffin\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic athlete\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"Gothamist\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just wanted to see if it could be done.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, I just kept going.\\\"\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's how she finally found Coup De Pates, a French food supplier whose website includedphotosof a very familiar looking muffin.\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1453, \"end\": 1459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9984673211741933, \"rank\": 0.0014363262866873485, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Coup De Pates\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"whose website\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1487}, {\"ngram\": \"a very familiar looking muffin\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But because of Coup De Pates' business-to-business model and its lack of a process for exporting to New York, Zhang could not just place an online order.\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1637, \"end\": 1645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999950175466872, \"rank\": 4.98243755619551e-06, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"business\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1587}, {\"ngram\": \"its lack\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"a process\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1619}, {\"ngram\": \"Zhang\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"an online order\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By then, Zhang had gotten the attention of food and dining site Eater, which contacted the company andconfirmedthat it worked with some \\\"partners of the Olympic Village.\\\"\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1845, \"end\": 1860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.90628330318865e-14, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zhang\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"the attention\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"food and dining site Eater\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1761}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1790}, {\"ngram\": \"some \\\"partners\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I put out an open call in the Eater piece as well as on TikTok just being like, 'Hey, does any restaurant or caf\\u00e9 or anything want to partner on this?\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.175593249773193e-38, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}, {\"begin\": 1974, \"end\": 1978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coffeehouse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0071196361683952e-23, \"text\": \"caf\\u00e9\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coffeehouse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coffeehouse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an open call\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1887}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eater piece\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1906}, {\"ngram\": \"any restaurant\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1970}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think there is an incredible opportunity here for the restaurant,'\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an incredible opportunity\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2058}, {\"ngram\": \"the restaurant\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I framed it in very capitalistic terms \\u2026 but really, I just wanted to try the muffin myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2190, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"very capitalistic terms\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"the muffin\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's where Angel Zheng, the owner of Isshiki Matcha and a frequent TikTok user herself, came in.\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2211, \"end\": 2216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"score\": 0.7862168799614816, \"rank\": 0.25921418621922104, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http: